            <div type="transcript" id="J480">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>"Why do I love" You, Sir?</l>
                    <l>Because --</l>
                    <l>The Wind does not require the Grass</l>
                    <l>To answer -- Wherefore when He pass</l>
                    <l>She cannot keep Her place.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Because He knows -- and</l>
                    <l>Do not You --</l>
                    <l>And We know not --</l>
                    <l>Enough for Us</l>
                    <l>The Wisdom it be so --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Lightning -- never asked an Eye</l>
                    <l>Wherefore it shut -- when He was by --</l>
                    <l>Because He knows it cannot speak --</l>
                    <l>And reasons not contained --</l>
                    <l>-- Of Talk --</l>
                    <l>There be -- preferred by Daintier Folk --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Sunrise -- Sir -- compelleth Me --</l>
                    <l>Because He's Sunrise -- and I see --</l>
                    <l>Therefore -- Then --</l>
                    <l>I love Thee --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
